name: MERCURY RETROGRADE 2021 - burnedbyairfryer #119 (1/1)
description:
My first (@burnedbyairfryer) minted piece on hicetnunc.xyz!

September 27-October 18, 2021 is when Mercury goes into retrograde for it's final time this year. A lot of things MIGHT go out of whack, but if you are cautious & observant of your actions, you may be able to prevent the solar system from f*cking up yo sh*t!

To be honest, I just learned about it this year, but hearing it's effects definitely had me intrigued. Here is my first impression of the concept in digital collage form. This piece is also another start of me revamping my style & use of multiple digital tools, therefore it has a special place in my being.

@burnedbyairfryer on instagram piece #119 (1/1 on tezos chain)
